("e6b692a8-3776-451e-864d-44092280846f","Faithful","You have advantage on Composure, Perception and Insight checks to stave off doubt, see through illusions, etc.","b47adc33-7171-46aa-843d-9713f1e250ba",NULL);
INSERT INTO `Backgrounds`(`id`,`title`,`description`,`skillsId`,`abilitiesId`,`settingsId`,`questions`) VALUES
("09d60eaa-9d79-4328-9729-d432cd205cdf","Merchant","In the markets and along the trade routes, you have carved a niche for yourself in the world of commerce. Whether through inherited trade connections, shrewd negotiation skills, or a natural knack for understanding the ebb and flow of markets, you’ve gained an understanding of your local economy that enables you to support yourself.","9fc5e86c-665d-44ea-8bbf-1b3ddd9bcd54","515e1331-adf8-467f-a196-4c848d6e43bb","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("143de443-a9b3-4440-ba9f-1439d369728e","Soldier","War has been your life for as long as you care to remember. You trained as a youth, studied the use of weapons and armor, learned basic survival techniques, including how to stay alive on the battlefield. You might have been part of a standing national army or a mercenary company, or perhaps a member of a local militia who rose to prominence during a recent war.","d4192952-a0ac-45bf-9403-3b0f0763e530","ceb69b2f-42ef-409d-b9f9-7dae9ea60ab2","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("235dcbb7-8333-440e-afb4-e9e8f9967964","Spirit-Blooded","Whether by circumstance of ","ce6554ff-c2e8-4672-af92-22307e8c8af1","b79ce121-e8fb-49b8-904c-d300a1498c7e","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("498890d8-1246-41a2-9c19-723a6a5696c0","Hermit","Isolated in the serene solitude of nature or the seclusion of a hidden retreat, you embraced a life of introspection. Whether seeking spiritual enlightenment, escaping the chaos of the world, or uncovering hidden truths, you withdrew from society to find solace in isolation. Your time spent away from civilization has granted you unique insights and skills, shaping you into a contemplative and self-sufficient individual.","810a3672-b911-47ae-9452-aa4a843bd7be","5ef90201-d601-4605-b4c0-b6814ffbdb1a","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("55fec94a-0ee0-4085-bc52-ff7816b2b7bb","Urchin","Born and raised in the unforgiving alleys, rooftops, and hidden corners of a sprawling city, you are an Urchin—a street-smart survivor, skilled in the art of navigating the urban jungle. Your childhood was a constant struggle for survival, forging your character in the crucible of adversity. Whether as a pickpocket, street performer, or messenger, your wits and resourcefulness have become your greatest assets.","bca6285f-2134-4e2e-99aa-5643cd67297f","f3d90b78-7b8d-4c50-b67b-2ff2767cff4a","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("578ee998-6302-49b3-afed-8c9447c3003d","Uplift","",NULL,"5ef90201-d601-4605-b4c0-b6814ffbdb1a","c6e57ee5-a805-4cff-ac88-76f779116b0e",""),
("5a7b908c-d9bd-4d2e-a2b6-b2b13ff24b73","Bioroid","",NULL,"f3d90b78-7b8d-4c50-b67b-2ff2767cff4a","c6e57ee5-a805-4cff-ac88-76f779116b0e",""),
("66a54a28-5fb6-4d43-8484-eafbdfc41f74","Courtier","Operating in the grand halls of power and the opulent courts of nobility, you are familiar with intrigue, diplomacy, and the fearsome minutiae of courtly manners. Born or raised in the corridors of influence, you have cultivated the art of navigating the complex web of social hierarchies, politics, and alliances that define the noble world. Your skills extend beyond the mere mastery of etiquette; you are a manipulator of perceptions and a wielder of influence.","c0d4ca7e-27d3-41da-baa3-08cefdc23e8a","5ef90201-d601-4605-b4c0-b6814ffbdb1a","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("66c2178b-7365-481c-a2cf-3f7d3f399cad","Entertainer","Whether your audience consists of the creme de la creme of high society or the common folk of your hometown, you’ve become adept at transporting them with the power of your performances. From the grand theaters of high society to the bustling taverns of the common folk, your skills have transcended mere amusement; they have become an integral part of who you are.","4c0961a0-b36b-4425-ad3d-d00cbf6f1f73","06911990-9f2d-494f-9d08-77c268d3c2ad","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("81cdc99f-85aa-4570-92e9-81b1e87dd7f2","Ghost","",NULL,"515e1331-adf8-467f-a196-4c848d6e43bb","c6e57ee5-a805-4cff-ac88-76f779116b0e",""),
("83c7f04e-d03f-478a-b7c2-04c173c640d7","Scholar","You spent years learning the lore of the multiverse. You scoured manuscripts, studied scrolls, and listened to the greatest experts on the subjects that interest you. Your efforts have made you a master in your fields of study.","d766b75d-c331-4204-a5bd-74342d9c97b9","515e1331-adf8-467f-a196-4c848d6e43bb","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("84eee503-96dc-44bc-b143-fb7cab8e3e71","Robot","",NULL,"b79ce121-e8fb-49b8-904c-d300a1498c7e","c6e57ee5-a805-4cff-ac88-76f779116b0e",""),
("8c87ce0c-5087-4d91-b5cc-ac927719f4ef","Laborer","Most of your life so far has been spent in the toil of fields, the clangor of forges, or the construction sites of burgeoning cities. Your life is one of manual labor, a commitment to shaping the physical world with strength and determination.","2f98193a-3e32-4273-bc5f-54b949e05e03","ceb69b2f-42ef-409d-b9f9-7dae9ea60ab2","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("ad5894cf-3bb8-448e-ab81-2086cdd722ea","Slave","In the dark corners of societal injustice, you emerged from the shackles of oppression, a survivor of a life marked by hardship and subjugation. The Slave background represents a character who has endured the harsh realities of forced labor, servitude, and the relentless struggle for freedom. Your past is scarred by the chains that bound you, but your spirit remains unbroken.","2ddf470b-75ea-4ca4-8c6a-8acd84531142","b79ce121-e8fb-49b8-904c-d300a1498c7e","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("b47adc33-7171-46aa-843d-9713f1e250ba","Acolyte","You have spent your life in the service of a temple to a specific god or pantheon of gods. You act as an intermediary between the realm of the holy and the mortal world, performing sacred rites and offering sacrifices in order to conduct worshipers into the presence of the divine. ","a3940fb4-1a63-4d3d-8a6e-981ac8c529a7","515e1331-adf8-467f-a196-4c848d6e43bb","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("bc3070f5-053c-4697-9285-162176812b05","Human","",NULL,"06911990-9f2d-494f-9d08-77c268d3c2ad","c6e57ee5-a805-4cff-ac88-76f779116b0e",""),
("c89bb383-dbe6-4d3f-8fd8-b973b7f5ff9c","Reaver","You are a warrior forged in the crucible of combat, driven by a primal need for glory and survival. Whether a former slave forced into the gladiatorial games or a willing combatant seeking fame, your skills with weapons and your ability to entertain the masses have defined your existence.","aefde7f4-dfa5-4588-965c-0a9a27766b4e","ceb69b2f-42ef-409d-b9f9-7dae9ea60ab2","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("d337469c-51a9-4e1b-ab60-3712745f1c28","Criminal","You are an experienced criminal with a history of breaking the law. You have spent a lot of time among other criminals and still have contacts within the criminal underworld. You’re far closer than most people to the world of murder, theft, and violence that pervades the underbelly of civilization, and you have survived up to this point by flouting the rules and regulations of society.","41f2bca1-7e61-4c4a-a18a-54ef2e5e5ea5","f3d90b78-7b8d-4c50-b67b-2ff2767cff4a","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("d98b8b77-41c4-49a5-99ac-eac4eba64904","Spy","In the shadowy realm of intrigue and covert operations, you emerged as a master of deception and espionage, navigating a web of secrets, manipulation, and danger. Your life is a delicate dance between loyalty and betrayal, as you navigate the intricate landscapes of political intrigue and clandestine operations.","1fa2dac5-59d3-4353-b8dc-1fb5d8f03c34","06911990-9f2d-494f-9d08-77c268d3c2ad","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("da0574c9-3355-4644-9618-3b44b355a095","Noble","You understand wealth, power, and privilege. You carry a noble title, and your family owns land, collects taxes, and wields significant political influence. You might be a pampered aristocrat unfamiliar with work or discomfort, a former merchant just elevated to the nobility, or a disinherited scoundrel with a disproportionate sense of entitlement. Or you could be an honest, hard-working landowner who cares deeply about the people who live and work on your land, keenly aware of your responsibility to them.","c002c2e2-b153-4cc1-b7cd-e6082280fe4f","06911990-9f2d-494f-9d08-77c268d3c2ad","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("db46f2ec-25ef-42d9-903c-70d1f88c5c8d","Scout","Hailing from the vast wilderness and the fringes of civilization, you are a master of survival, stealth, and reconnaissance. Whether serving in a military unit, acting as a guide for travelers, or navigating the untamed wilds as a lone wanderer, your skills in tracking, observation, and swift movement make you an indispensable asset in the great outdoors.","29b03a16-ea6e-436d-8dd1-442322ca6bee","5ef90201-d601-4605-b4c0-b6814ffbdb1a","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("ec0c372c-eb8b-46cb-b064-c4883096e482","Artisan","In quiet workshops, bustling forges, and secluded studios, you have honed your skills of creation. You might be a blacksmith, a painter, or even an alchemist. You likely apprenticed in your chosen craft as a youth— perhaps you’ve risen to the rank of master by now, or perhaps you’re a journeyman.","4e229802-ec97-4144-93ff-0ae863e98eb2","b79ce121-e8fb-49b8-904c-d300a1498c7e","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84",""),
("f00bb8eb-d5cb-492b-8052-af4dc8fc9aab","Doped Shell","",NULL,"ceb69b2f-42ef-409d-b9f9-7dae9ea60ab2","c6e57ee5-a805-4cff-ac88-76f779116b0e",""),
("f2aec8db-e632-4257-ab79-f6514f6270c8","Sailor","You are a seasoned mariner who has navigated treacherous waters and weathered the storms that would send lesser souls to their doom. The rhythmic creaking of the ship, the salt-laden breeze, and the call of distant gulls are the constants of your life. Whether a pirate, a naval officer, or a humble deckhand, the sea has etched its mark on your character, forging you into a stalwart and adaptable adventurer.","f254212e-572a-41ca-9686-917387297673","f3d90b78-7b8d-4c50-b67b-2ff2767cff4a","54007770-4641-4ce8-8265-dc24b23cab84","");
